{"tid":50734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強迫亂倫】「我阿媽想搞我」 正義仔難忍多次要求捅死親母","createTime":"2016-12-22T16:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T23:52:44.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d52d11b946ff422abf387835373cdfc3af7ae167","tid":50734,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161222/large/1482407259_2ae9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161222%2Flarge%2F1482407259_2ae9.jpg&h=1972e3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尼日利亞奧貢州（Ogun State）一名33歲男子，在家中用菜刀殺死母親，他聲稱是因為母親不斷要求與他做愛而感厭惡，無法忍受下殺人尋求解脫。<br />\n<br />\n弒母的奧岡勒斯（Segun Ogunlusi），本月13日走進家中廚房，拿起菜刀刺入60歲母親阿賓博拉（Abimbola）的腹部，對方當場死亡。他稱：「我將煤油淋在她屍體上想燒屍，但屍體無法燃燒，於是我便將屍體棄於水渠，我後悔自己所做的一切。」<br />\n<br />\n奧岡勒斯作供時聲稱，阿賓博拉過去不斷強迫他亂倫，他已多次警告對方要打消這念頭，但母親仍未罷休，「我殺死我母親，因她不斷要求與我做愛，她說如果我與她做愛，我就可以自由。」他無法接受，便趁只有兩人在家時"},{"pid":"fe79acbe96f41e6d81cc8a600cee54ab49c3ebf9","tid":50734,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:13:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f42ce67619f778dfc377247e92d9045fe4be7a68","tid":50734,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:15:06.000Z","msg":"新聞未出完喎"},{"pid":"7f19ae1f0d6ade5a6794887c06c269cf61879213","tid":50734,"uid":17240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:17:25.000Z","msg":"強迫影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3458dd88f46432695ba5b98b1eb30f5f778d02a","tid":50734,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"60路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405dfe338db103e677effdfde409652eae4647c9","tid":50734,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161222/large/1482407259_2ae9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161222%2Flarge%2F1482407259_2ae9.jpg&h=1972e3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尼日利亞奧貢州（Ogun State）一名33歲男子，在家中用菜刀殺死母親，他聲稱是因為母親不斷要求與他做愛而感厭惡，無法忍受下殺人尋求解脫。<br />\n<br />\n弒母的奧岡勒斯（Segun Ogunlusi），本月13日走進家中廚房，拿起菜刀刺入60歲母親阿賓博拉（Abimbola）的腹部，對方當場死亡。他稱：「我將煤油淋在她屍體上想燒屍，但屍體無法燃燒，於是我便將屍體棄於水渠，我後悔自己所做的一切。」<br />\n<br />\n奧岡勒斯作供時聲稱，阿賓博拉過去不斷強迫他亂倫，他已多次警告對方要打消這念頭，但母親仍未罷休，「我殺死我母親，因她不斷要求與我做愛，她說如果我與她做愛，我就可以自由。」他無法接受，便趁只有兩人在家時行兇。<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"343204a110a06eadde8b4ce10859719df43152e8","tid":50734,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:21:30.000Z","msg":"黑人黎講算靚仔"},{"pid":"d91b867ffbebc758ffd5eae0bc7aff71d18dfe20","tid":50734,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑人黎講算靚仔</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去重慶大廈行轉先"},{"pid":"a0e9bfaaf40ccda0d2759a6eab4928890ab1d730","tid":50734,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0244b99bc853a17b1e8764e35a23a6482e55932","tid":50734,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T23:39:29.000Z","msg":"33歲仲要同母親一齊住"},{"pid":"ae587639347677f87b7d10143638ca31877df95a","tid":50734,"uid":60572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"